txt.en: 'I noticed posters blowing through the Cisterns filled with lies from the Withered Tree. You must find their camps in the Cisterns and destroy their fear-mongering papers.'
The Withered Tree can be found in the Cisterns.\n\nYou should find and destroy documents belonging to the Withered Tree.
The Withered Tree has taken hold of the Cisterns and it is up to you to destroy their lies.
